{"timestamp":1774427727390,"source_app":"agentic-harness","session_id":"4c0db3ed-78d0-4fb4-87b9-5c5270699359","hook_event_type":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_use_id":"toolu_016WV39JpouzSKGspj9T47j9","payload":{"session_id":"4c0db3ed-78d0-4fb4-87b9-5c5270699359","transcript_path":"/Users/auto/.claude/projects/-Users-auto-agentic-harness-apps-mas-trees-bdf67753/4c0db3ed-78d0-4fb4-87b9-5c5270699359.jsonl","cwd":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/bdf67753","permission_mode":"bypassPermissions","hook_event_name":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/bdf67753/specs/patch/patch-missing-variant-and-trial-id-coverage.md","content":"# Patch: Add missing variant and trial ID test coverage in processCTAs\n\n## Metadata\nadw_id: ``\nreview_change_request: `Issue #2: Test coverage omits plans-education and plans-students variants and three trial IDs (start-free-trial, fourteen-day-trial, thirty-day-trial), leaving the Set membership unvalidated by tests. Resolution: Add test cases for the missing variants and trial analytics IDs to fully cover the PLANS_VARIANTS and FREE_TRIAL_CTA_IDS constants. Severity: tech_debt`\n\n## Issue Summary\n**Original Spec:** specs/issue-bdf67753-adw-1d78f7d6-sdlc_planner-hide-free-trial-ctas-plan-pages.md\n**Issue:** The `processCTAs` describe block in `web-components/test/hydrate.test.js` validates filtering for the `plans` and `plans-v2` variants and the `free-trial` and `seven-day-trial` analytics IDs, but leaves `plans-education`, `plans-students`, `start-free-trial`, `fourteen-day-trial`, and `thirty-day-trial` completely untested. Both `PLANS_VARIANTS` and `FREE_TRIAL_CTA_IDS` in `hydrate.js` therefore have members whose filtering behaviour is unvalidated.\n**Solution:** Add five focused `it()` test cases to the existing `processCTAs` describe block: two to verify that `plans-education` and `plans-students` trigger filtering, and three to verify that `start-free-trial`, `fourteen-day-trial`, and `thirty-day-trial` analytics IDs are removed on a plans variant.\n\n## Files to Modify\n\n- `web-components/test/hydrate.test.js` \u2014 append five `it()` blocks inside the existing `processCTAs` describe block (after the last test at line 327).\n\n## Implementation Steps\n\n### Step 1: Add test \u2014 plans-education variant filters trial CTAs\nAdd an `it()` block that passes a CTA with `data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\"` and calls `processCTAs` with variant `'plans-education'`. Assert the footer is empty (CTA was filtered).\n\n- CTA HTML: `<a is=\"checkout-link\" data-wcs-osi=\"abm\" data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\" class=\"accent\">Free Trial</a>`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'plans-education')`\n- Assert: `footer.children` has length `0`\n\n### Step 2: Add test \u2014 plans-students variant filters trial CTAs\nAdd an `it()` block with the same CTA HTML but variant `'plans-students'`. Assert the footer is empty.\n\n- CTA HTML: `<a is=\"checkout-link\" data-wcs-osi=\"abm\" data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\" class=\"accent\">Free Trial</a>`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'plans-students')`\n- Assert: `footer.children` has length `0`\n\n### Step 3: Add test \u2014 start-free-trial analytics ID is filtered on plans variant\nAdd an `it()` block with a CTA whose `data-analytics-id` is `\"start-free-trial\"` and variant `'plans'`. Assert the footer is empty.\n\n- CTA HTML: `<a is=\"checkout-link\" data-wcs-osi=\"abm\" data-analytics-id=\"start-free-trial\" class=\"accent\">Start Free Trial</a>`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'plans')`\n- Assert: `footer.children` has length `0`\n\n### Step 4: Add test \u2014 fourteen-day-trial analytics ID is filtered on plans variant\nAdd an `it()` block with `data-analytics-id=\"fourteen-day-trial\"` and variant `'plans'`. Assert the footer is empty.\n\n- CTA HTML: `<a is=\"checkout-link\" data-wcs-osi=\"abm\" data-analytics-id=\"fourteen-day-trial\" class=\"accent\">14-Day Trial</a>`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'plans')`\n- Assert: `footer.children` has length `0`\n\n### Step 5: Add test \u2014 thirty-day-trial analytics ID is filtered on plans variant\nAdd an `it()` block with `data-analytics-id=\"thirty-day-trial\"` and variant `'plans'`. Assert the footer is empty.\n\n- CTA HTML: `<a is=\"checkout-link\" data-wcs-osi=\"abm\" data-analytics-id=\"thirty-day-trial\" class=\"accent\">30-Day Trial</a>`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'plans')`\n- Assert: `footer.children` has length `0`\n\n## Validation\nExecute every command to validate the patch is complete with zero regressions.\n\n```bash\n# From the web-components directory\ncd /Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/bdf67753/web-components\nnpx wtr test/hydrate.test.js --node-resolve\n```\n\nAll five new test cases should pass, and all previously existing `processCTAs` tests must continue to pass.\n\n## Patch Scope\n**Lines of code to change:** ~50\u201365 lines added (five `it()` blocks)\n**Risk level:** low\n**Testing required:** Run `web-components/test/hydrate.test.js`; verify all existing and new `processCTAs` tests pass with zero regressions.\n"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_016WV39JpouzSKGspj9T47j9"}}
